## Post-snapshot orchestration

`tools/run_post_snapshot_supervisor.py` runs after daily pipeline:
- Checks all 13 steps completed
- Triggers supervisor anomaly detection
- Updates knowledge layer
- Generates operator brief

## Anti-patterns

- Do NOT run screen without cache warm (stale 8-K data)
- Do NOT reduce timeout below 6000s (Monday AACT kills it)
- Do NOT modify cron entries without verifying they survive WSL restart
- Do NOT merge PRs with failing CI unless budget-blocked (not code-broken)
- Do NOT skip the test wrapper (bare pytest misses env normalization)